<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1102243.What_Hath_God_Wrought"><img alt="What Hath God Wrought: The Transformation of America, 1815 - 1848" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1440944879l/1102243._SX98_.jpg" />
