<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/42201377-the-pioneers"><img alt="The Pioneers: The Heroic Story of the Settlers Who Brought the American Ideal West" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1556447325l/42201377._SX98_.jpg" />
